data.description: Recently updated, beautiful brick home in the quiet country. Located 8 minutes from Metter, 10 minutes from I-16, 15 minutes to portal, and 20 minutes to Statesboro. Home features split floorplan, large master bedroom, and open kitchen. Spacious back porch area with plenty of room for company and having a good time. This home has lots to offer and is a must see.
